helptext HAND_VALVE_HELP = "HAND VALVE

----------

This object has two possible states it can display, either open or closed. This is represented by:


Green Foreground - OPEN


White Foregroud - CLOSED



MENU OPTIONS

------------

If the valve is closed then the menu option is to dressed the valve open, whereas if the valve is open then the menu option is to dress the valve closed.


NB, This object is purely for displaying the valve status and serves no control functions whatsoever.
"
